@startuml
title Send Proactive Notification Sequence Diagram

actor Administrator
participant "Dashboard Script\n(public/js/script.js)" as Script
participant "API Server\n(src/server.js)" as Api
participant "Orders Store\n(src/orders.js)" as Orders
participant "WhatsApp Client" as WhatsApp
actor Customer

Administrator -> Script : Change order status
Script -> Api : PUT /api/orders/:id {status}
Api -> Orders : updateOrder(id, updates)
Orders --> Api : updated order + oldStatus
Api -> Api : status changed?
Api -> WhatsApp : sendMessage("Status changed to ...")
WhatsApp --> Customer : Proactive status message
Api --> Script : success response

note right of Api
If WhatsApp delivery fails, the status remains updated
and the error is logged asynchronously.
end note

@enduml
